{"tid":564472,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有沒有人覺得上天對自己很不公平?","createTime":"2018-02-18T04:34:46.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-18T07:49:55.000Z","uid":27553,"like":14,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"5da2bb28e65d8aa66cd96ada58d1127599ed6723","tid":564472,"uid":27553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-18T04:34:46.000Z","msg":"自己出身草根,係屋村仔,不要說李嘉誠的兒子,或是有錢人的家庭,中產也不能<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n沒有錢,不要緊,如果父母對自己好,教導有方,也可以的.但父母常找自己出氣,不講道理,常常埋怨,常常批評,這樣的父母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n人天生漂亮,總有一定的優勢,但為什麼自己不是<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n好吧!如果天生聰明醒目,做事學習事半功倍,也好!但為什麼我的IQ比一般人還要低一點(做過一些基本可信的測試)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n上天對自己很不公平<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但我不服氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n幸好我心永遠不死,讓自己找到轉機,看著吧!<br />\n看著我怎樣扭轉這些不公平吧!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n你們覺得上天對你公平嗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"652956d77f14f337d2c138897d19e52796a22893","tid":564472,"uid":28277,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-18T04:38:23.000Z","msg":"其實唔公平比公平多，睇得開就得"},{"pid":"c86718898a2b44be038fde966d11a9e8086fdc9b","tid":564472,"uid":29314,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-18T04:40:33.000Z","msg":"呢個世界邊度有公平過？"},{"pid":"ab6b711cb42205d67582c1e7dd9d6acb1f3ecbca","tid":564472,"uid":67500,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-18T04:48: